<li>Massoud, Amy, 2016. &ldquo;Moral Worth and Supererogation,&rdquo;
<em>Ethics</em>, 126: 690&ndash;710.</li>

<li>McDowell, John H., 1998. <em>Mind, Value, and Reality</em>,
Cambridge, MA: Harvard University Press.</li>

<li>McHugh, Conor, &amp; Jonathan Way, 2016. &ldquo;Fittingness
First,&rdquo; <em>Ethics</em>, 126: 575&ndash;606.</li>

<li>Meacham, C., 2013. &ldquo;Impermissive Bayesianism,&rdquo;
